snippet.title: Shelter Generations Gameplay Trailer [Nintendo Switch - ESRB]
snippet.description:
Take a look at gameplay from Shelter 2 and Paws, which are both included in Shelter Generations on Nintendo Switch; it arrives on the Switch eShop on 12th April.
